e engine, the power to the cigarette lighter is also cut off, causing the dash cam to stop recording.<br><br>To overcome this limitation and ensure continuous power supply to your dash cam, you can opt for a <b>hardwire kit</b>. A hardwire kit allows you to directly connect your dash cam to the vehicle's electrical system, providing a more reliable and uninterrupted power source.

